local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["prehistoric"]={"prehistoric","[priːhɪ'stɒrɪk]","[,prihɪ'stɔrɪk]","adj.史前的",'adj.史前的','The study of the forms of life existing in prehistoric or geologic times, as represented by the fossils of plants, animals, and other organisms.','古生物学对出现在史前或地质时代的生命的形成的研究，体现在植物、动物和其它有机体的化石上','Some prehistoric people lived in caves.','有些史前时期的人住在洞穴里。'}
